<div class="cms-copy-rsp" >
    
        <p>There are several ways you can stop direct marketing communications from us:</p>
<ul style="list-style-position: inside;">
<li>Click the âunsubscribeâ link in any email communication that we send you. We will then stop any further emails from that particular division.</li>
<li>If you have an account, log in into your John Lewis or Waitrose account, visit the âMy Accountâ area and change your preferences.</li>
<li>In our apps, you can manage your preferences and opt out from one or all of the different push notifications by selecting or deselecting the relevant options in the âSettingsâ section.</li>
<li>Write to<b>&nbsp;Group Customer Insight (Customer Data), Partnership House, 1st Floor, Carlisle Place, London SW1P 1BX</b>.</li>
</ul>
<p>Please note that you may continue to receive communications for a short period after changing your preferences while our systems are fully updated.</p>

    
