<div class="cms-copy-rsp" >
    
        <p><b>14.1 How we use your personal data</b></p>
<p>When you purchase a product or service from John Lewis Finance, we might receive a copy of the information you supplied. If you agree to receive marketing communications from us, we will use your data to personalise what we send you. You are free to opt out of receiving marketing communications from us at any time.</p>
