<p>We may check your details with appropriate third parties (for example credit reference agencies, such as Experian) before we send you promotions for our financial services products, to ensure your information is accurate and fulfils our legal and regulatory obligations, and to tailor those offers to you.</p>
<p>Rest assured that all applications for financial services products will be assessed on a case-by-case basis.</p>

    
