    <section class="  cms-accordion-item2 cms-accordion-item2--no-padding">
  <h2 class="cms-accordion-item2__title"><span>17. Any questions?</span></h2>

  <div class="cms-accordion-item2__description">
  <div class="cms-grid-container">
    <div class="col"
  aria-hidden="false"
>

<div class="cms-divider-rsp cms-divider-whitespace-medium"></div>
</div>


<div class="col col-lg-12 offset-lg-0"
  aria-hidden="false"
>

<div class="cms-copy-rsp" >
    
        <p>We hope this Privacy Notice has been helpful in setting out the way we handle your personal data and your rights to control it.</p>
<p>If you have any questions that havenât been covered, please contact our Data Protection Officer who will be pleased to help you:</p>
<ul style="list-style-position: inside;">
<li>Email us at&nbsp;<b>DPO@johnlewis.co.uk</b><br>
</li>
<li>Or write to us at&nbsp;<b>Data Protection Officer, Partnership House 1st Floor, Carlisle Place, London SW1P 1BX</b></li>
</ul>
<p>This notice was last updated on 05/06/2018<br>
